 lead you to the druid gathering.<br>7, Kill the Dark Elf Corruptor and Reavers that spawn and loot the Fleshbound Tomb.<br>8, Give the Fleshbound Tomb to Althele to get the Earth Stained Note <br>9, Go to Misty Thicket. Give the Earth Stained Note to Ella Foodcrafter to get the Shiny Tin Bowl. <br>Create the Hardened Mixture<br><br>1, Go to Everfrost and forage the Chilled Tundra Root <br>2, Go to Greater Faydark and forage the Ripened Heartfruit <br>3, Go to Innothule Swamp and forage the Speckled Molded Mushroom <br>4, Go to Misty Thicket and forage the Sweetened Mudroot <br>5, Place the Chilled Tundra Root, Ripened Heartfruit, Speckled Molded Mushroom, and Sweetened Mudroot in the Shiny Tin Bowl. Hit the Combine button to create the &quot;Hardened Mixture <br>Runecrested Bowl Ingrediant #1 [Ancient Pattern]<br><br>1, Go to Timorous Deep. Talk to Alrik Farsight and say ‘I will take the artifact' to get the Crushed Pot. <br>2, Go to Felwithe <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> . Give the Crushed Pot to Farios Elianos to get the Grocery List. <br>3, Go to Felwithe [A]. Give the Grocery List to Merchant Nora to get the Bag of Provisions. <br>4, Go to Felwithe <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> . Give the Bag of Provisions to Farios Elianos Receipt. <br>5, Go to Timorous Deep. Give the Receipt to Alrik Farsight to get the Ancient Pattern. <br>Runecrested Bowl Ingrediant #2 [Platinum Speckled Powder]<br><br>1, Go to Firiona Vie and forage a Rose of Firiona. <br>2, Go to Surefall Glade. Give Merdan Fleetfoot the Rose of Firiona to get the Wood Painting. <br>3, Go to Frontier Mountains. Give the Wood Painting to the Human Skeleton to get the Silver Chained Locket.<br>[Note: Spawns around NEG 2100, POS 200<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 0] --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/alien.gif ALT="0]"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>4, Go to Surefall Glade. Give the Silver Chained Locket to Niera Farbreeze to get the Platinum Speckled Powder. <br>Runecrested Bowl Ingrediant #3 [Enchanted Clay]<br><br>1, Go City of Mist. Kill a Black Reaver to get a Jade Reaver.<br>[Note: This item is tradeable.] <br>2, Go to Kaladim <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> . Give the Jade Reaver to Kinlo Strongarm to get the Enchanted Clay. <br>Create the Runecrested Bowl<br>1, Combine the Ancient Pattern, Enchanted Clay, and Platinum Speckled Powder in a Pottery Wheel to make a Runecrested Bowl.<br>[Note: This requires no skill in pottery to do and any pottery wheel should work.]<br>The Elaborate Scimitar<br><br>1, Go to Misty Thicket. Give the Hardened Mixture and Runecrested Bowl to Ella Foodcrafter to get the Softly Glowing Stone. <br>2, Go to Karnor's Castle. Kill Venril Sathir to spawn Venril Sathirs remains. <br>3, Cast the spell Dance of the Fireflies to Summon a Firefly Globe. <br>4, Give the Firefly Globe to Venril Sathirs remains to spawn the Spirit of Venril Sathir. <br>5, Give the spell Ressurection [Level 49 Cleric Spell] to the Spirit of Venril Sathir to respawn Venril Sathir. <br>Kill Venril Sathir to get the Pulsing Green Stone. <br>6, Go to Firiona Vie. Give the Softly Glowing Stone and the Pulsing Green Stone to Foloal Stormforest to get the Warmly Glowing Stone. <br>7, Go to Misty Thicket. Give Ella Foodcrafter the Warmly Glowing Stone to get the Elaborate Scimitar. <br>Cleansed Spirit of Antonica<br><br>1, Go to Everfrost. Kill the Corrupted Mammoth to get the Chunk of Tundra. <br>2, Go to Lake Rathetear. Kill the Corrupted Aqua Goblin Shaman to get the Clean Lakewater. <br>3, Go to Rathetear Mountains. Kill the Corrupted Hill Giant to get the Ancient Rock. <br>4, Go to North Karana. Give the Chunk of Tundra, Clean Lakewater and Ancient Rock to the Withered Treant to get the Warm Pulsing Treant Heart. <br>5, Go to South Karana. Give the Warm Pulsing Treant Heart to Yeka Ias to get the Cleansed Spirit of Antonica. <br>Cleansed Spirit of Faydwer<br><br>1, Go to Kedge Keep. Kill the Corrupted Seahorse to get the Kedge Cave Crystals. <br>2, Go to the Ocean of Tears. Kill the Corrupted Cyclops to get the Ocean of Tears Seavines. <br>3, Go to Lesser Faydark. Kill the Corrupted Brownie to get the Green Heartwood Branch. <br>4, Give the Kedge Cave Crystals, Ocean of Tears Seavines and Green Heartwood Branch to the Pained Unicorn to get the Gleaming Unicorn Horn. <br>5, Go to Ak'Aknon. Give the Gleaming Unicorn Horn to Silox Azrix to get the Cleansed Spirit of Faydwer. <br>Cleansed Spirit of Kunark<br><br>1, Go to the Swamp of No Hope. Kill Ulump Pujik to get the Froglok Essence. <br>2, Go to the Emerald Jungle. Kill the Corrupted Gorilla to get the Green Tree Bark. <br>3, Go to the Lake of Ill Omen. Kill the Corrupted Barracuda to get the Pure Lakewater. <br>4, Go to Timorous Deep. Give the Froglok Essence to Dolgin Codslayer to spawn Faydedar. He will return the Froglok Essence to you. <br>Kill Faydedar to get the Pod of Seawater. <br>5, Go to Overthere. Give the Froglok Essense, Green Tree Bark, Pure Lakewater and Pod of Seawater to Nekexin Virulence to get the Cleansed Spirit of Kunark. <br><br>Nature Walkers Scimitar<br>Go to North Karana. Give the Elaborate Scimitar, Cleansed Spirit of Antonica, Cleansed Spirit of Faydwer and Cleansed Spirit of Kunark to Xanuusus to get the Nature Walkers Scimitar.<br><br>PS. I hope this is complete, it may not be every little detail.  I pulled it f</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <p>Markis <BR><BR><BR>Hit'em Fast<BR>Hit'em Hard</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm12.showPrevMessage?topicID=5.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm12.showNextMessage?topicID=5.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdra